Top Downloads Menu
--------------------------------

1. Info
	This menu will show your latest 5 (or whatever you like)
	downloads on your e107 system. You can choose the downloads'
	category, how many downloads and for what period (week, month)
	to be shown.
	
	Ex.: This week's top 5 downloads; This month's top 15 downloads

2. Istallation
	No installation needed.
	Just unpack the archive into your plugins dir.
	Activate the menu through the Menu manager.
	The config page is accessible through the config opion
	in the dropdown menu in Menu manager